title: Music in my head < music of the senses.
pid: 54a69ba6-725c-4398-b342-b9a18e197c72
body: |2-
  When there's music in my head I miss the figurative music of the world, the sensory detail. Those details are better -- more complex, more interesting, more variegated. The music in my head is usually a short repeating melody.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
